LexRAG: Multi-Agent Legal Document Q&A System

• Built a production-grade RAG pipeline with LangChain + Ollama (Mistral-7B): semantic chunking, HuggingFace em
beddings, ChromaDB vector store with MMR retrieval, achieving 91% retrieval accuracy over 500+ page legal corpora.
• Designed a multi-agent architecture (router → retrieval → critic) using LangChain AgentExecutor for self-correcting,
citation-grounded answers with explicit hallucination flagging; evaluated via RAGAS across 200 automated prompts.
